com.qmetry.qaf.automation.ui.webdriver

Class ByJQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openqa.selenium.By
      • com.qmetry.qaf.automation.ui.webdriver.ByJQuery

  • public class ByJQuery
extends org.openqa.selenium.By
    com.qmetry.qaf.automation.ui.webdriver.ByJQuery JQuery strategy locator strategy for application where JQuery used in client side implementation. If JQuery is not used, then either a direct connection or a proxy setting is needed to access https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery in order for the JQuery JS to be retrieved.
    Author:
    chirag.jayswal
